---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Fun — JZ Stafura"
  description="Experiments, toys, and diversions."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="overline">Fun</p>
    <h1>Experiments &amp; Diversions</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Not everything has to be serious. Some things exist because they should.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="grid">
    <a href="/fun/banana-santana/" class="card">
      <div class="card-emoji">🍌</div>
      <h2>Banana Santana Name Generator</h2>
      <p>Six absurdist naming algorithms. Rhyming pairs, quasi-European aristocrats, celebrity mashups, nicknamed characters, and more. Each with a 65% chance of an occupation.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Pure JS</span>
          <span class="tag">Absurdist</span>
        </div>
        <span class="card-cta">Generate a name &#x2192;</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/fun/soulwrap/" class="card card-dark">
      <div class="card-emoji">&#x1F32B;</div>
      <h2>SoulWrap&#x2122;</h2>
      <p>A deadpan luxury wellness landing page for a fictional existential crisis solution. The aesthetic is serious. The joke doesn&#x2019;t wink.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Parody</span>
          <span class="tag">Vanilla HTML</span>
        </div>
        <span class="card-cta">Visit site &#x2192;</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/fun/valinor-capital/" class="card card-vc">
      <div class="card-emoji">&#x2694;&#xFE0F;</div>
      <h2>Valinor Capital</h2>
      <p>A parody venture capital firm backing founders who refuse to inherit broken systems. Tolkien-themed. Underground city portfolio. The investment thesis is airtight.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Parody</span>
          <span class="tag">Tolkien</span>
          <span class="tag">Vanilla HTML</span>
        </div>
        <span class="card-cta">Visit firm &#x2192;</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/fun/dramaturgical-slam/" class="card card-slam">
      <div class="card-emoji">&#x1F3AD;</div>
      <h2>Dramaturgical Slam</h2>
      <p>Erving Goffman&#x2019;s dramaturgical sociology staged as a one-night-only pro-wrestling card. The Idealized Self vs. the Self Off Duty. Front stage. Back stage. No refunds on the self.</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Parody</span>
          <span class="tag">Goffman</span>
          <span class="tag">Vanilla HTML</span>
        </div>
        <span class="card-cta">Enter the arena &#x2192;</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .overline { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .hero { padding: 4rem 0 3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-muted); }

  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(340px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }

  .card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: #FFAA00;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(255, 170, 0, 0.12);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .card-dark:hover {
    border-color: #9ca3af;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .card-vc { background: #070B14; border-color: #1C2238; }
  .card-vc:hover {
    border-color: #B8962E;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(184, 150, 46, 0.12);
  }
  .card-vc h2 { color: #E4DFD5; }
  .card-vc:hover h2 { color: #D4AF50; }
  .card-vc p { color: #8A8780; }
  .card-vc .tag { color: #8A8780; border-color: #1C2238; }
  .card-vc .card-cta { color: #B8962E; }

  .card-slam { background: #5A0B12; border-color: #7A1620; }
  .card-slam:hover {
    border-color: #E3AE3C;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(227, 174, 60, 0.15);
  }
  .card-slam h2 { color: #ECE0C6; }
  .card-slam:hover h2 { color: #F6D27C; }
  .card-slam p { color: #DCCBA4; }
  .card-slam .tag { color: #DCCBA4; border-color: #7A1620; }
  .card-slam .card-cta { color: #E3AE3C; }

  .card-emoji { font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }

  .card h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: normal; color: var(--color-text); transition: color 0.15s; }
  .card:hover h2 { color: #d97706; }
  .card-dark:hover h2 { color: var(--color-text); }

  .card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.7; flex-grow: 1; }

  .card-footer { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

  .tags { display: flex; gap: 0.4rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .tag { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 0.15rem 0.45rem; }

  .card-cta { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #d97706; }
  .card-dark .card-cta { color: var(--color-muted); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
